
<% if @payments.length > 1 %>
  <h2>You have <%= @payments.length %> new PorkCasts!</h2>
<% else %>
  <h2>You have a new PorkCast!</h2>
<% end %>
<br>


<h3><p>On <%= Date.today.strftime("%d/%m/%Y") %> Your page on PorkCast has been updated to show new payments the State of Montana made to your queries. Below is a summary, Go to the main <%= link_to "PorkCast", "http://www.porkcast.com" %> website to check it out!</p></h3>

<table>
  <thead>
    <th>Payee</th>
    <th>Amount</th>
    <th>Payment Date</th>
  </thead>
 <tbody style="border:solid black 2px">
    <% @payments.each do |payment| %>
      <tr style="border:solid black 2px">
        <td><%= payment[0] %></td>
        <td>$<%= sprintf( "%0.02f", payment[1]) %></td>
        <td><%= payment[2].strftime("%d/%m/%Y") %></td>
      </tr>

    <% end %>
 </tbody>
</table>

<p><em>This email was sent to <%= @user.email %>. To unsubscribe from this PorkCast log in and disable notifications for this or all PorkCasts at  <a href="http://www.porkcast.com">http://www.porkcast.com</a></em></p>

<em>

  <br>In 2016 we plan on launching our next big release of PorkCast, which will include:
