  <ul>1000x times larger database (if the state ever deletes data, we will have a fully intact latest version of the data preserved)</ul>
  <ul>Registration free browsing (for folks who want to search, but do not want payment notifications) </ul>
  <ul>A sleek interface that is geared for easier use on iPads and smartphones</ul>
  <ul>Lightning fast query speed</ul>
  <ul>PDF and Excel Report Exporting</ul>
  <ul>Upgrades to our PorkCast <a href="http://www.twitter.com/porkcast">twitterbot</a></ul>

<p>If you have further ideas on features you would like to see in the 2.0 release, we would love to hear from you at this email!</p>
